edu.stanford.math.plex4.streams.utility

Class FilteredComparator<M>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.math.plex4.streams.utility.FilteredComparator<M>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - the underlying type of the basis elements
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<M>

    public class FilteredComparator<M>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<M>
    This class provides filtration based comparison of basis elements. It implements a dictionary ordering where first the filtration indices are compared, and then the actual basis elements are compared using the supplied comparator.
    Author:
    Andrew Tausz
